g noisy inputs, and finally, by a simple\nmodel in which binary activations of a multiplicity of input channels produce a\ndynamic response that closely approximates the dynamics of a prescribed linear\nsystem whose inputs are continuous functions of time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 00:59:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 18:53:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
