cts. Nevertheless, the bias in\nparameter estimation of spin for the limited spin prior range can be a clue of\nthe existence of superspinars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 04:18:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 07:50:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
