ated. Moreover, it is likely that the grid operator induces\nimbalances to the system by incomplete redispatch activation (i.e. upward and\ndownward redispatch volumes are not equal).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 08:47:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-12"}
