One and Wiki-One. Compared with the strong baseline model MetaR, our model\nachieves 5-shot FKGC performance improvements of 8.0% on NELL-One and 2.8% on\nWiki-One by the metric Hits@10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2021 10:38:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 02:56:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
